  • Classes in org.bukkit.attributes used by org.bukkit.attributes 
    Class and Description

    AttributeModifier
    A numerical transformation that can be applied to the values of Attributes.
    AttributeModifier.Operation 
    AttributeValue
    The state of a particular Attribute for a particular LivingEntity, consisting of a base value and a set of AttributeModifiers.
